OL,3,CGunman shot dead by police after at
OL,4,Cleast six killed in Kyiv shooting
OL,6,FA gunman who killed at least six
OL,7,Fpeople in the streets of Kyiv has been
OL,8,Fshot dead by police, Ukrainian
OL,9,Fofficials said.
OL,11,FThe gunman opened fire before taking
OL,12,Fhostages and barricading himself in a
OL,13,Fnearby supermarket on Saturday.
OL,15,FHead of Ukraine's Interior Ministry
OL,16,FIhor Klymenko said in a statement on
OL,17,Fsocial media that special tactical
OL,18,Fpolice units stormed the store after
OL,19,Fattempts to contact the gunman with a
OL,20,Fnegotiator failed. The attacker was
OL,21,Fkilled while resisting arrest, he said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/5
