OL,3,CGunman shot dead by police after at
OL,4,Cleast six killed in Kyiv shooting
OL,6,FSpeaking to reporters at the scene,
OL,7,FKlymenko said that the government had
OL,8,Fkilled four bystanders while on the
OL,9,Fstreet, before entering the
OL,10,Fsupermarket and killing a fifth person.
OL,12,FMayor Vitali Klitschko said that a
OL,13,Fsixth victim, a young woman, had died
OL,14,Ffrom her injuries in the hospital.
OL,16,FPresident Volodymyr Zelenskyy said at
OL,17,Fleast ten people had been
OL,18,Fhospitalised. Among those hospitalised
OL,19,Fwas at least one child, Klitschko said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/5
