OL,3,CGunman shot dead by police after at
OL,4,Cleast six killed in Kyiv shooting
OL,6,FThe shooting took place in Kyiv's
OL,7,FHolosiivskyi district, Mayor Vitali
OL,8,FKlitschko said.
OL,10,FTelevised footage of the scene showed
OL,11,Fpolice taking cover in the shopping
OL,12,Fmall that housed the supermarket while
OL,13,Fshots were fired. Bystanders were
OL,14,Fescorted away from the scene.
OL,16,FSpeaking to reporters at the scene,
OL,17,FUkraine's interior minister provided
OL,18,Fno speculation as to the assailant's
OL,19,Fmotives, but said that police
OL,20,Fnegotiators spoke with the attacker
OL,21,Ffor roughly 40 minutes.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/5
