OL,3,CGunman shot dead by police after at
OL,4,Cleast six killed in Kyiv shooting
OL,6,F"We tried to persuade him, knowing
OL,7,Fthat there was likely a wounded person
OL,8,Finside. We even offered to bring in
OL,9,Ftourniquets to stop the bleeding, but
OL,10,Fhe did not respond," Klymenko said.
OL,11,F"Consequently, the order was given to
OL,12,Fneutralise him."
OL,14,FKlymenko, who wore body armour, said
OL,15,Fthe man was carrying a carbine rifle,
OL,16,Fwhich was legally registered.
OL,18,F"In December of last year, 2025, he
OL,19,Fapproached the licensing authorities
OL,20,Fto have the weapon test-fired as the
OL,21,Fpermit was expiring.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOUtD@PO]zD@AOU
