OL,3,CGunman shot dead by police after at
OL,4,Cleast six killed in Kyiv shooting
OL,6,F"He provided a medical certificate. He
OL,7,Fhad also submitted an application to
OL,8,Frenew his permit for the weapon. That
OL,9,Fis all we can say for now," Klymenko
OL,10,Fsaid.
OL,12,FHe added that the investigation will
OL,13,Fdetermine which medical institution
OL,14,Fissued the certificate.
OL,16,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,17,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,18,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,19,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,20,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,21,Fbelow...
